{% extends 'base/base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}

{% endblock %}

{% block stylesheets %}

{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

<style>
    :root {
        --dark-navy: #0a192f;
        --accent-gold: #c5a059;
        --text-silver: #e6f1ff;
    }
    .hero-section {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #112240 0%, var(--dark-navy) 100%);
        color: var(--text-silver);
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    }
    .glass-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.2);
        padding: 4rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
    }
    .summary-label {
        color: var(--accent-gold);
        text-uppercase: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .summary-value {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.2);
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .btn-gold {
        background-color: transparent;
        color: var(--accent-gold);
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-gold);
        letter-spacing: 0.4rem;
        transition: all 0.4s;
        padding: 1rem 3rem;
    }
    .btn-gold:hover {
        background-color: var(--accent-gold);
        color: var(--dark-navy);
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.3);
    }
</style>

<div class="hero-section min-vh-100 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center py-5">
    <div class="glass-card shadow-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="h6 text-uppercase mb-5" style="color: var(--accent-gold); letter-spacing: 0.5rem; opacity: 0.8;">
            - Prologue -
        </h2>

        <div class="text-start px-md-4">
            <div class="summary-label">Player Name</div>
            <div class="summary-value">Yuya IKEDA</div>

            <div class="summary-label">Selected Shelf</div>
            <div class="summary-value">ROMANCE</div>

            <p class="small mb-5 italic" style="color: rgba(230, 241, 255, 0.6); line-height: 1.8;">
                傷の痛みを知らない奴は、他人の傷をあざ笑う。待て、何だろう、あの窓から射してくる光は？
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="mt-2">
            <p class="small mb-4" style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-style: italic;">
                舞台の準備は整いました。
            </p>
            <a href="" class="btn btn-gold text-uppercase fw-bold">
                Start
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5">
            <a href="" class="text-muted small text-decoration-none" style="opacity: 0.5;">
                ← 選択し直す
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{% endblock %}

{% block javascripts %}

{% endblock %}
